      "text": "うん、それが足りないものだから",
      "startTime": 116.732708732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "パートナーがいてくれた方が、自然に笑えるし",
      "startTime": 121.3993743655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　役だからね！",
      "startTime": 125.5660298582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "パートナーの『役』！　誤解しないでよね！",
      "startTime": 128.5593825016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
